              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*En-rsl*.Because of the different energy losses of Li-6",
                "and He-6 particles in matter, the energy resolution",
                "is mainly limited by the thickness of the targets."
              ]
            }
          ],
